\b About
\b0 \
\
Syphon is a system for sending video between applications. You can use it to send high resolution and high frame rate video, 3D textures and synthesized content between your Unity 3D scene and other applications.\
\
Syphon for Unity includes a plugin, scripts for both client and server and a few sample scenes to get you started. \

